This game is created using Pygame library for Python.
To play this game you should have Python installed in your computer, and also pygame.
To download and install Python go to   https://www.python.org/downloads/
To install pygame go to your computers commandline or terminal and use the commands given in    https://www.pygame.org/wiki/GettingStarted

                                              
